  Chok-chia2 E5 Oe7 
  Ti7 che7-che7 khun3-lan5 e5 tiong-kan Seng3-kek8 te7-si3-chip8 koh iong2-kam2 lai5 chhut-pan2, in-ui7 pun2-lang5 sin-the2 khiam3 an, sou2-i2 keng-koe3 chit8-ni5 ku2 e5 leng2-chong5, ti7 kin-ni5 chiah koh hu3 in3. TaN pun2-chip8 si7 Seng3-keng kou3-su7 sou2 kai2-phian e5, sui si7 thong-siok8 iau2 ku2 chin seng5-tong7 pek-chin, ti7 thak8 e5 si5 chiu7 hou7 lang5 kam2-kak chhu3-bi7 ong2-ek8. 
  Keng-koe3 kui2-ni5 ku2 e5 tu3-chok keng-giam7, sou2-i2 pi2-kau3 cheng5 e5 chok-phin2 ia7 si7 khah chhiong-sit8 lau2-lian7. Chit e5 kek8-pun2 m7-na7 kan-ta sek-hap8 ti7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 kau3-hoe7 lou7-eng7, na7 cho3 thok8-pun2 ia7-si7 chin ho2, koh kin7-lai5 kong-po3 su7-kong e5 hoat-tian2, na7 li7-eng7 cho3 kong-po3 oa7-kek8 e5 lou7-eng7 si7 chin ho2. Ti7 pun2-lang5 e5 chok-phin2 tiong long2 si7 u7 chin beng5-hian2 e5 bok8-tek kap tiong-sim, chiu7-si7 hou7 lang5 bat Ia5-sou, chi2 u7 beng5-khak e5 chu2-te5 kap tiong-sim, chiah oe7 thang hun-beng5 chong-kau3 bun5-ge7 e5 tek8-sek, che7-che7 chok-phin2 chhin-chhiuN7 u7 hun7-loan7 chit e5 su7, sou2-i2 chin siok8-khi3 bo5 u7 giam5-siok e5 khi3-hun, ng3-bang7 lan2 ti7 tai5-teng2 beh ian2 e5 si5, ia7 oe7 thang tui3-tiong7 hit e5 goan5 chok-chia2 e5 cheng-sin5. 
