  好的撒瑪利亞人 二幕 
  人物 : 撒瑪利亞人 希百、猶太人 巴拿、巴拿之父 迦米、巴拿之妻 西西拉、祭司 約西、利末人 謝拉、強盜 a、強盜 b。 
  第一幕 
  出場人物:迦米 西西拉 巴拿 
  場 面:一個猶太的窮家庭裡，奧後有一位患病臥床的老人，右前面一中年小婦背嬰孩正在織布。 
  開 幕:老人臥在床上嗽喘吟呻著，小婦人一面搖背後 的小孩一面織布。 
  1. 迦米 : (Na2 sau3 na2 li7-hai7, chiu7 khi2-lai5 che7 ti7 chhng5-teng2)Ai-ah,thiN-khi3 iu7-koh tng2 leng2 lah(嗽且喘),chin tho2-iam3, m7-chai beh koh koaN5 kau3 ti7-si5 chiah oe7 chun2-sng3(嗽). 
  2. 西西拉: (站起來,走近老人) A-pa, li2 an2-ni kan-khou2 hiah ku2, bo5 chhiaN2 i-seng lai5 khoaN3 peN7 si7 boe7 eng7-tit lah (loah8 lau7-lang5 e5背後). ThiaN kong2 Ia5-lou7-sat-leng2 u7 chit8-ui7 chin gau5 e5 i-seng, kio3-choe3 Ma2-kiat, lan2 lai5 khi3 chhiaN2 i lai5 khoaN3 peN7 m7-chai ho2 bo5? 
  3. 迦米: Mih-sai2 tioh8 an2-ni long7-hui3, lan2 e5 ka-teng5 ia7 m7 si7 teh ho2-koe3, saN-tng3 to teh boe7 kou3-tit, pang3 chhut-chai7 i khi3.(嗽且喘). 
  4. 西西拉: A-pa, li2 long2 si7 an2-ni kheh-khi3, Chu2 Ia5-ho-hoa tek-khak oe7 thoe3 lan2 khui-lou7, bo5-lun7 an2-choaN2 bo5 chhiaN2 i-seng lai5 khoaN3 si7 boe7 eng7-tit. 
  5. 迦米: Chu2 Ia5-ho-hoa na7 si-loh8 chu5-pi, kin2 tiau3 goa2 e5 leng5-hun5 kui7 ti7 goa2 e5 chou2, an2-ni chiu7 m7-bian2 ke-thiN lin2 e5 tang7-taN3 kap khun3-lan5, hou7 lin2 u7 chian5-tou5 e5 ng3-bang7(嗽且喘), goa2 an2-ni bo5 si2 si7 chin thoa-lui7 tioh8 lin2. 
  6. 西西拉: A-pa, chhiaN2 li2 m7-thang an2-ni kong2, Pa-na2 kap goa2 long2 chin su-iau3 li2, li2 tui3 goan2 u7 chin toa7 e5 pang-chan7 kap chi2-to7, (khoaN3 eN-a2) Iok-han7 ma7 chin ai3 A-kong, li2 u7 kap goan2 ti7 teh goan2 chiah u7 khoai3-lok8 kap heng7-hok. 
  7. 迦米: To-sia7, Se-se-lah8, goa2 chai-iaN2 Pa-na2 kap li2 e5 hau3-sun7, che si7 goa2 ti7 chit e5 khun3-khou2 e5 jin5-seng tiong choe3 toa7 e5 an-ui3. Goan7 Siong7-te3 po3-tap lin2, lai5 su3-hok lin2. TaN ho2, taN ho2, goa2 khah khuiN3-oah8 lah, m7-bian2 koh lo5-hoan5 li2 lah. (西西拉放手,老人行倚台前,西西拉扶之). 
  8. 西西拉 : A-pa, li2 chheng7 an2-ni u7 kau3 sio bo5? Li2 ai3 lim tam7-poh8 sio-te5 bo5? 
  9. 迦米: Se-se-lah8, li2 m7-bian2 ui7-tioh8 goa2 khoa3-lu7 sim2-mih8, goa2 i2-keng hou7 li2 kau3-giah8 siu7-khou2 lah. Li2 an2-ni bo5 chit8-si5-khek e5 an-hioh teh chit-pou3, pang-chan7 ka-teng5, sit8-chai7 hou7 li2 kau3-giah8 lo5-khou2, goa2 sit8-chai7 chin boe7 koe3-sim. 
  10.西西拉: A-pa, li2 long2 si7 kong2 hit-khoan2 kheh-khi3 oe7, che long2 boe7 thang sng3 choe3 sim2-mih8 lo5-khou2. Goa2 chin hoaN-hi2 an2-ni cho3 kang, ui7-tioh8 lan2 chit ke, ui7-tioh8 beh chheng7 chit-nia2 saN e5 lang5. (回到原位,再開始織布,老人行倚小婦的機邊) 
  11.迦米: Chin sui2, chin bi2-biau7 e5 sek-ti7! Tak8 e5 soaN3-kat long2 u7 thiaN3 kap cheng5 e5 ki3-ho7, chheng7 chiah e5 saN e5 lang5 sit8-chai7 u7 hok-khi3. 
  12.西西拉: Goa2 chit-nia2 chit liau2 chiu7 saN-nia2 lah; chit saN-nia2 si7 beh sang3 hou7 A-pa e5 le2-mih8. 
  13.迦米: Li2 kong2 an2-ni si7 sim2-mih8 i3-su3? 
  14.西西拉: Chiong chit saN-nia2 saN sou2 be7 e5 chiN5 khi3 chhiaN2 i-seng, theh8 ioh8, ng3-bang7 A-pa koaN2-kin2 ho2 khi2--lai5. 
  15.迦米: Boe7 eng7-tit, goa2 bo5 un2-chun2 li2 an2-ni choe3! Eng7 li2 e5 sim-huih lai5 cho3 goa2 e5 ioh8-chiN5, oh, goa2 leng7-khou2 si2, ia7 bo5 ai3 lin2 ui7-tioh8 goa2 an2-ni hi-seng, che kan-ta si7 hou7 goa2 e5 peN7 na2 tim5-tang7.(嗽且喘) 
  16.西西拉 : A-pa, chhiaN2 li2 kin2-kin2 khi3 to2-leh, an2-ni siuN leng2 lah! (扶助老人到床邊,且撫他背後). A-pa, li2 m7-thang an2-ni kheh-khi3, goan2 khoaN3 li2 an2-ni kan-khou2 si7 chin siong-sim. 
  17.迦米: An2-ni ho2 lah, jin5-seng chong2-si7 lo5-lok8 khou2-thang3, an2-ni ho2 lah, bo5 iau3-kin2 lah.(西西拉停手). Pa-na2 thai2 iau2 boe7 tng2-lai5? Chiah nih8 koaN5 soaN-ia2 e5 pak-hong si7 chin leng2. 
  18.西西拉: A-pa, li2 kin2 to2 leh, m7-bian2 khoa3-lu7 Pa-na2, i phah-sng3 liam5-piN oe7 tng2-lai5 lah.(老人臥床,小婦給他施棉被,然後回到原位,開始織布. 巴拿出場) 
  19.巴拿: (解他覆在頭上的布,和背後的羊皮) Chin koaN5, chin koaN5, soaN-ia2 e5 hong na2 to oe7 koah lang5 e5 bah, lian5 iuN5-kun5 tioh8 siuN7 beh tng2-lai5 tiau5-lai7 bih sio.(去探嬰孩) Iok-han7 li2 oe7 koaN5 boe7?! Hiah nih8 kou2-chui teh khun3.(問西西拉) A-pa an2-choaN2, u7 khah ho2 se3 bo5? 
  20.西西拉: Sau3 kau3 chin li7-hai7 koh chin chhoan2, goa2 siuN7 bo5 chhiaN2 i-seng si7 boe7 eng7-tit, chit pai2 si7 pi2 i2-cheng5 khah siong-tiong7 e5 khoan2. 
  21.巴拿: Goa2 siuN7 ia7 si7 tioh8 chhiaN2 i-seng (沉默片刻). Chong2-si7 beh an2-choaN2 siat-hoat ioh8-chiN5?! Boe7 lan2 sou2 u7 e5 iuN5, che si7 choat8-lou7, a-pa it-teng7 m7-kheng2, boe7 liau2 bin5-a2-jit8 khi2 chiu7 bo5 u7 iuN5-mng5 thang be7 lah. 
  22.西西拉: Pa-na2, li2 chin sio2-sin3, Siong7-te3 kiam2 oe7 pang3-sak lan2 mah! (西西拉拿織布起來)Li2 thang chiong chiah e5 saN theh8 khi3 be7 lai5 oaN7 ioh8 chiN5. 
  23.巴拿: Chit-pai2 kiam2 m7 si7 ui7-tioh8 lan2 chit ke e5 lang5 sou2 chit e5 saN? An2-ni kiam2 oe7 eng7-tit, lan2 e5 saN long2 chin ku7 lah?! 
  24.西西拉: U7 sim2-mih8 boe7 eng7-tit, goa2 oe7-thang koh khai-si2 lai5 chit, kin-ni5 e5 koaN5-thiN bo5 thang chheng7, lan2 khah jim2-siu7 leh, kau3 me5-ni5 chiu7 u7 thang chheng7 lah. 
  25.巴拿: (接衣布過來) Chit liau2 chin sui2, an2-ni si7 chin hi-seng li2! Se-se-lah8, goa2 chin kam2-kek li2 e5 thiaN3. (吻衣服) 
  26.西西拉: (微笑,後來開始整理織機) ThiaN kong2 u7 chit8 ui7 Sat-ma2-li7-a e5 seng-li2 lang5, kio3 choe3 Hi-pek choan-bun5 kiaN5-seh8 ti7 chit e5 si3-hng teh be2-chip8 hu7-jin5-lang5 sou2 chit e5 saN, lan2 thang chhoe7 hit e5 lang5 lai5 be7 hou7 i. 
  27.巴拿: Sat-ma2-li7-a lang5 Hi-pek!? An2-ni si7 boe7-eng7-tit, li2 kiam2 m7-chai lan2 e5 chong-chok8 si7 choat8-tui3 bo5 kap Sat-ma2-li7-a lang5 lai5-ong2, a2-si7 choe3 be2-be7, che si7 kian3-siau3 e5 su7, bu2-jiok8 lan2 chou2-sian e5 mia5-siaN. 
  28.西西拉: Pa-na2, chit khoan2 e5 siuN7 hoat si7 choe3 kho2-lin5 e5 phian-kian3, choe3 gu5-gong7 e5 koan-liam7, Sat-ma2-li2-a lang5 kiam2 m7 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-lui7? Kiam2 m7 si7 Iu5-thai3 lang5 e5 kut-jiok8? 
  29.巴拿: Sat-ma2-li7-a lang5 si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 khi3-sak e5, si7 poe7-gek8 e5 kiaN2. Lan2 e5 chou2 Tai7-pit8 e5 ong5-kok chiu7-si7 hou7 in chhiuN2-toat8 khi3, lai5 ti3-kau3 hun-li7, Sat-ma2-li7-a lang5 si7 lan2 e5 kiu-siu5! Si7 lan2 e5 tui3-tek8! Bo5-lun7 ju5-ho5 lan2 choat8-tui3 bo5 kap in lai5-ong2, lan2 ia7 iam3-chian7 hia e5 kap in lai5-ong2 e5 lang5. 
  30.西西拉: Che si7 jin5-lui7 pi-kek8 choe3 mau5-tun2, choe3 thang siong-sim e5 chho3-gou7, goa2 boe7 thang li2-kai2 chit khoan2 e5 kiu-oan si7 cheng3-tong e5 su7. (老人由床起身) 
  31.迦米: Goa2 ng3-bang7 Chu2 Ia5-ho-hoa kin2 hou7 goa2 si2, m7-thang ti3-kau3 hou7 goa2 e5 kiaN2-sun kiaN5 tioh8 hoan7-hoat e5 lou7, goa2 choat8-tui3 bo5 un2-chun2 lan2 khi3 kau chhap jim7-ho5 e5 Sat-ma2-li7-a lang5, in-ui7 in si7 poe7-gek8 pai7-lou7 e5 kiaN2-ji5, lan2 e5 chou2 i2-keng siu7-chin7 liau2 in e5 khun3-khou2 lah, li2 chai sim2-mih8 lang5 pho3-hai7 lan2 e5 chou2 tui3 chhian-khou2 ban7-khou2 sou2 kian3-lip8 nng7-chheng goa7 ni5 Hi-pek-lai5 ong5-kok e5 bin5-bang7?! Kiam2 m7 si7 Sat-ma2-li7-a lang5 e5 chou2-sian. Sim2-mih8 lang5 lian5-hap8 put-sin3 e5 goa7-pang lai5 kong-kek, kiau2-jiau2 lan2 e5 chou2 kap seng3-siaN5 Ia5-lou7-sat-leng2!? Kiam2 m7 si7 khou2-ouN3 e5 Sat-ma2-li7-a lang5!? Ui7 sim2-mih8 ian5-kou3 Tai7-pit8 e5 ong5-kok kin-a2-jit8 chiaN5-cho3 chit khoan2 e5 pai7-loh8, hou7 goa7-pang lang5 cho3 chiah8-mih8, siu7 chin7 in e5 leng5-jiok8 kap khun3-khou2 ah? Chiu7-si7 Sat-ma2-li7-a lang5 e5 chou2 e5 poe7-poan7! Lan2 e5 chou2 chiu3-choa7 bo5 beh koh kap Sat-ma2-li7-a lang5 ong2-lai5, chhui3-khi2 poe5 chhui3-khi2, bak8-chiu poe5 bak8-chiu! Lan2 ng3-bang7 u7 chit8 jit8, chit e5 poe7-poan7 e5 jin5-bin5 oe7 tu2-tioh8 Chu2 Ia5-ho-hoa e5 toa7 siu7-khi3 lai5 biat8-bong5! 
  32.西西拉: A-pa, goa2 boe7 thang li2-kai2, sui-jian5 si7 an2-ni, goa2 boe7 thang li2-kai2 ti7 lan2 e5 chou2-sian sou2 cho3 e5 tai7-chi3, u7 koan-he7 ti7 lan2 kap Sat-ma2-li7-a lang5 Hi-pek e5 su7. Lan2 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2, chong2-si7 Sat-ma2-li7-a lang5 ia7 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 soan2-bin5, Sat-ma2-li7-a lang5 na7 siu7 khi3-sak lai5 biat8-bong5, che kiam2 m7 si7 lan2 e5 pi-ai kap hoan5-lo2, lan2 si7 tang5 chit8 e5 chou2-sian e5 kut-jiok8, tang5 chit8 e5 Siong7-te3 e5 soan2-bin5, tang5 mia7-un7 e5 tong5-pau. 
  33.迦米: Se-se-lah, goa2 chong2 bo5 siuN7 tioh8 li2 ti7 chit chan5 su7 hou7 goa2 chiah-nih8 siong-pi koh cho3 that-gai7, an2-ni goa2 beh an2-choaN2 tui3-tit-khi2 goa2 e5 chou2-sian!! (嗽且喘) 
  34.巴拿: Se-se-lah, li2 bo5 eng-kai koh giau5-gi5, in-ui7 che si7 thoan5-thong2, si7 ui7-beng7, lan2 chi2 u7 tioh8 ke3-siok8 lan2 e5 chou2 sou2 hou7 lan2 e5 cheng-sin5.(向迦米) A-pa li2 sou2 kong2 e5 si7 tioh8, goan2 tek-khak bo5 ui5-poe7 li2 e5 i3-su3, chhiaN2 li2 pang3-sim, ia7 kin2-kin2 to3 leh hioh-khun3, m7-thang koh koaN5 tioh8. 
  35.(老人臥床,嗽且喘真利害) 
  36.西西拉: (對巴拿) Na7 si7 an2-ni lan2 iau2 u7 sim2-mih8 hoat-tou7 thang tit-tioh8 chiN5?! A-pa hiah-nih8 kan-khou2 bo5 kin2-kin2 chhiaN2 i-seng si7 boe7 eng7-tit. 
  37.巴拿: (SiuN7 bo5 pan7-hoat teh沉思) Kiam2 m7 si7 iau2 u7 chit8 e5 Ia5-li7-ko lang5 kio3 choe3 Sui-li7 iu5-goan5 teh siu be2 chit khoan2 e5 pou3-kiaN7 mah?! Lan2 thang chhoe7 i lai5 be7 hou7 i! 
  38.西西拉: (Chhin-chhiuN7 chin sit-bang7 koh kiaN5-oa2 khi3 beh siu-sip8 i e5織器) Sui-li7 u7 teh ka7 lang5 be2, chong2-si7 i2-keng chiaN5-geh8-jit8 bo5 koh khoaN3 i ti7 Ia5-lou7-sat-leng2 lah, m7-chai u7 sim2-mih8 pian3-tong7. 
  39.巴拿 : (Kat-bak8 koh沉想) An2-ni goa2 toa3 chiah e5 saN lai5 khi3 Ia5-li7-ko chhoe7 i, bo5 an2-ni cho3 si7 boe7 kai2-koat, goa2 chit-tiap sui5-si5 chhut-hoat, an2-ni kim-me5 goa2 chiu7 oe7 thang kau3 hia, ti7 bin5-a2-jit8 tiong-tau3 goa2 chiu7 oe7-thang koh to3-tng2-lai5 lah. (khai-si2 koh teh chheng7 phoe5-saN, 西西拉tioh8-kiaN). 
  40.西西拉: Sim2-mih8! Li2 beh khi3 Ia5-li7-ko!? Pa-na2, li2 kiam2 m7-chai Ia5-li7-ko e5 lou7-chiuN7 chin gui5-hiam2,siong5-siong5 u7 kiong5-to7 bai5-hok8 ti7 soaN-kan teh chhiuN2-kiap lang5,sat-hai7 lang5! Li2 kiam2 thang an2-ni choe3? Ho5-hong3 chit e5 si5-chun7 i2-keng beh am3 lah, Pa-na2 li2 ui7-tioh8 goan2 e5 ian5-kou3 m7-thang an2-ni choe3! 
  41.巴拿: Che si7 ui7-tioh8 a-pa choe3-au7 e5 chit8-tiau5 lou7, goa2 ng3-bang7 Chu2 Ia5-ho-hoa bo5 pang3-sak lan2, lan2 e5 chou2 ki3-jian5 chiu3-choa7 bo5 beh kap Sat-ma2-li7-a lang5 ong2-lai5, lan2 tioh8 tam7-poh8 chiah8-khou2 ia7 koat-toan3 m7-thang u7 sou2 ui5-poe7 sian-jin5 e5 cheng-sin5. (chheng7 ho2-se3 koh pak8 thau5-kin) 
  42.西西拉: Pa-na2, lan2 kiam2 bo5 u7 pat8 e5 hoat-tou7? Li2 beh khi3 Ia5-li7-ko goa2 e5 sim chin boe7 thang pang3-sim, koh bo5 it-teng7 li2 chhoe7 oe7 tioh8 Sui-li7, kiam2-chhai2 li2 chhoe7 oe7 tioh8 i, chong2-si7 i i2-keng kai2-giap8 oaN7-chit lah, Pa-na2 li2 koh siuN7-khoaN3 an2-ni thai3 gui5-hiam2, lan2 kiam2 bo5 pat8 e5 hoat-tou7? 
  43.巴拿: Se-se-lah8, li2 kiam2 boe7 ki3-tit Chu2 Ia5-ho-hoa si7 lan2 ti7 hoan7-lan7 tiong kip-si5 e5 pang-chan7? Na7 u7 chhut su7, Siong7-te3 tek-khak oe7 kiaN5 ki5-su7 sin5-jiah lai5 chin2-kiu3, li2 tioh8 pang3-sim, goa2 bin5-a2-jit8 chiu7 oe7 tng2-lai5 lah, na7 chhoe7 bo5 Sui-li7 lan2 chiah koh phah-sng3 pat8 e5 hoat-tou7. 
  44.西西拉: Goa2 iu5-goan5 chin boe7 hiau2 li2-kai2! Siong7-te3 kiam2 ai3 I e5 kiaN2-ji5 in-ui7 hou7-siong phau7-oan3 lai5 chiah8 bo5 eng-kai chiah8 e5 khou2, che si7 gu5-gong7 kau3-kek8, chin-li2 kiam2 si7 seN cho3 an2-ni?! 
  45.巴拿: Li2 iu7 si7 chit e5 khoan2-sit! Lan2 iam3-chian7 Sat-ma2-li2-a lang5, che si7 kin-pun2 e5 cheng-sin5! Lan2 iam3-chian7 in, m7-kiaN sim2-mih8 sun2-sit kap hi-seng! Goa2 tek-khak tioh8 khi3 Ia5-li7-ko, che bo5 thang koh kho2-lu7, Se-se-lah8, li2 tui3 goan2 thai3 ho2 chhiaN2 li2 m7 thang koh u7 sim2-mih8 giau5-gi5, chhiaN2 li2 an-sim lai5 tan2-hau7 goa2, ho2-ho2 chiau3-kou3 a-pa, goa2 beh lai5--khi3 lah! 
  46.西西拉: Goa2 i2-keng chai-iaN2 goa2 bo5 hoat-tou7 thang chou2-tong3 li2, goa2 chi2 u7 chiong li2 kau-thok ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 chhiu2, goa2 tek-khak thong-me5 ui7 li2 ki5-to2 tit8-kau3 koh khoaN3 li2 e5 bin7, ng3-bang7 Siong7-te3 toa3-nia2 li2, po2-siu2 li2 chit8-lou7 peng5-an. Pa-na2 chhiaN2 li2 tioh8 khah sio2-sim leh! (Pa-na2 chim eN-a2, khoaN3 西西拉chiu7退場,西西拉心情恐懼不安sang3 i ti7 門口, au7-lai5 kui7 teh ki5-to2). 
